heaviest_rainrate.status: The rain rate reached 27.0mm per hour on 02 September 2025, and resulted in 21.19mm of rain over 15.0 hours.  This is the highest rate recorded by our weather station.

summary.description:
Today, cooler for the feels like temperature (down 5.5°C), outside temperature (down 4.9°C), and inside temperature (down 2.8°C) and drier conditions in rainfall (down 0.1 mm).

Compared to today, yesterday also had noticeable differences in cloud levels (up 140 m).

The past week and month had observable variation in feels like temperature (up 7.0°C), dew point temperature (up 5.5°C), outside temperature (up 6.4°C), and cloud levels (up 312 m) when compared to today.
